lect specific content as much as possible. long','',1,NULL,NULL,'2025-02-20 14:16:46','2025-02-20 14:16:46'),(2606,'1044','App\\Models\\Subsection','Tables',NULL,'',3,'67b73d3eb18ff.png','/storage/tables/67b73d3eb18ff.png','2025-02-20 14:16:46','2025-02-20 14:33:34'),(2607,'1044','App\\Models\\Subsection','Text','When preparing a presentation, it is important to have a variety of charts to present as the basis for your argument. Charts are very important element in the presentation, as the appropriate form must be selected according to the characteristics of the item to be displayed to make the audience understood and convinced of VOI rouma Most of the charts fall into the five types below You should use the chart well according to your message','',1,NULL,NULL,'2025-02-20 14:16:46','2025-02-20 14:16:46'),(2608,'1045','App\\Models\\Subsection','Tables',NULL,'<Table 26  Basic Patterns of Visualization',2,'67b73d3ebbfe7.png','/storage/tables/67b73d3ebbfe7.png','2025-02-20 14:16:46','2025-02-20 14:33:34'),(2609,'1045','App\\Models\\Subsection','Text','Visualization is a way of using schematics to better understand the subject, and appropriate schematics is much more effective than writing verbosely: For visualization, the items go through the process of structuring the message using the following pattern: using','',1,NULL,NULL,'2025-02-20 14:16:46','2025-02-20 14:16:46'),(2610,'1046','App\\Models\\Subsection','Text','First Principle: With a suitable structure-Selection of shape types according to the description method of keywords Second Principle: Easy to understand-structured logic for intuitive understanding Third Principle: Highlight points-Highlight to be emphasized with color or other shapes points','',1,NULL,NULL,'2025-02-20 14:16:46','2025-02-20 14:16:46'),(2611,'775','App\\Models\\Section','Figures',NULL,'',1,'67b73d3ec75a3.png','/storage/figures/67b73d3ec75a3.png','2025-02-20 14:16:46','2025-02-20 14:33:34'),(2612,'776','App\\Models\\Section','Tables',NULL,'',