re keys in plaintext for ease of access.\", \"Generate keys without a specific algorithm.\", \"Share keys among all employees for convenience.\"]','2025-03-28 01:40:51','2025-03-28 01:40:51'),(2451,4,'Test','A recent incident involving unauthorized access to a database has raised concerns about the effectiveness of existing access control measures. Assess the current access control policies in place and recommend improvements. What specific criteria should be considered to ensure that access controls are both effective and compliant with regulations?',1,3.5,'Very Hard','C4-Zuf1CMa7TtSCq5FFhGWlHA','Multiple Choice - Single','\"Implement Role-Based Access Control (RBAC) and regular audits.\"','[\"Implement Role-Based Access Control (RBAC) and regular audits.\", \"Maintain the current policies without changes.\", \"Limit access to only one employee.\", \"Increase access privileges for all users.\"]','2025-03-28 01:40:51','2025-03-28 01:40:51'),(2452,4,'Test','During an evaluation of a database encryption strategy, a company discovers that it has been using an insecure hashing algorithm for password storage. Critique the current approach and recommend a secure hashing strategy. What justifications can you provide for your recommendation based on potential vulnerabilities?',1,3.4,'Very Hard','C4-53KxB5khSdCiFTY41vzZ7Q','Multiple Choice - Single','\"Implement SHA-256 with a SALT value.\"','[\"Implement SHA-256 with a SALT value.\", \"Continue using the current hashing algorithm.\", \"Use no hashing for password storage.\", \"Switch to an even older hashing method.\"]','2025-03-28 01:40:51','2025-03-28 01:40:51'),(2453,4,'Test','A company is considering the implementation of a network sniffing method for monitoring database access. Evaluate the potential advantages and disadvantages of this method compared to agent-based and gateway methods. What would you recommend as the best approach for ensuring robust database security?',1,3.4,'Very Hard','C4-y7DqH3svTEu9QpYIivA7rQ','